_Globalizado_[ informs [es]](http://arellanos.blogspot.com/2010/07/dia-del-
pollo-la-brasa.html) his readers that July 18 is Peruvian Chicken day ([“pollo
a la brasa”](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pollo_a_la_Brasa) in Spanish). It is
the first time that Peruvians celebrate this day in honor of a dish which the[
National Institute of
Culture](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/National_Institute_of_Culture) considers
one of the culinary specialties of
Peru[](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/National_Institute_of_Culture). The
blogger includes videos of news reports on the new holiday.

